      "corrected_page_text": "• 여과기능\nRenal Corpuscle\n• Glomerulus Glomerulus capsule 가을밀고들어감\n-> parietal layer + (capsular space) + visceral layer\n• Capsular space Renal corpuscle 혈액에서여과된액이에모임\n-> Renal corpuscle Proximal convoluted tubule 에가장가까운로감\n: 검은색혈액의흐름\n: 초록색여과액의흐름\n혈관많은부분\nTubule 이시작되는부분\n[Macula densa]\nThick ascending limb이\nRenal corpuscle afferent arteriole 자신의중에서도과가까운부분\n-Parietal layer : simple squamous epithelium\n-Visceral layer : ( ) podocyte여과위해특수분화된형태\nvisceral layer => Podocyte여과를위한특수\n-Proximal convoluted tubule : 부터\n- 발이문어처럼뻗어있음\n: simple columnar simple cubodial epithelium또는\n- 3종류가지\nprimary\n컴리워anerular celli\n-primary Pedicel 는붕떠있고이혈관의\nsecondary\nbasement membrane 에맞닿아있음\nprimary 에서나옴\n-Pedicel Podocyte primary 이다른의\nprocess Pedicel 의끼리깍지끼듯배열\n> 이 사이 간격이 Filtration slit (Filtration pore)\nprimary\n혈관과비슷한\n방향으로나옴\n• layer 여과는모세혈관과그사이에서일어남\n-layer = podocyte",
